Author: GitHub
Title: The best moments from GitHub Universe 2025
Description:
"Dream it in the morning, build it in the afternoon." This is the spirit of GitHub Universe 2025. We celebrated record growth (one developer a second!), the fun of the community, and the future of AI with Agent HQ. The energy was special, and we're already planning for next year.
